com.xing.api.data.profile

Class Address

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xing.api.data.profile.Address
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Address
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Java representation of an address object. Primary used for the XingUser model, to represent the user's business nad private addresses.
    See Also:
    Private Address Resource, Serialized Form
